name: Scare PewDiePie
overview: In this reality-adventure series from the creator and executive producers of "The Walking Dead," experience thrills, chills, and laughter as PewDiePie encounters terrifying situations inspired by his favorite video games.

episodes.name: Level 1 - Let's Play Doctor
episodes.overview: PewDiePie takes a trip to the clinic to see if he is capable and well enough to participate in shows of scares and frights. What he doesn't know is that the crazy things that happen there are all part of the first assignment.

episodes.name: Level 2 - We're Not Alone
episodes.overview: The US government needs a Swede to save the day. I’m going to save the world from an alien invasion with my bro Markiplier. Let’s do this.

episodes.name: Level 3 - Hello Timmy
episodes.overview: In pewdiepies second task, him and his friend mark attempt to survive outer space, in the mother ship where aliens are lurking.

episodes.name: Level 4 - Time to Die Mr. Pie
Level 5 - Please Enjoy Your Stay
episodes.overview: From Q and A to meat maze. This is the YouTube life I’m living. Someone get me out please!

episodes.name: Level 6 - The Ultimate Hang
episodes.overview: A man with a chainsaw is trying to kill me. Can I hide well enough to escape?

episodes.name: Level 7 - I'm Not Crazy
episodes.overview: Pewdiepie's 7th task is here and this time he will go on a trip through a mental hospital, where he will run into mental patients and scares.

episodes.name: Level 8 - Call of Pewdie
episodes.overview: PewDiePie participates in a tactical operation in which he is given orders to infiltrate and recover an objective from his most hated and feared enemies: barrels.

episodes.name: Level 9 - Naughty Pie
episodes.overview: Cross-dressed as a maid, PewDiePie is dragged around a house by raging and edgy maniacs to solve a bizarre goal: finding himself.

episodes.name: Level 10 - Game Over
episodes.overview: PewDiePie relaxes at a party and reminisces his past thrills throughout the season. But one memory in particular comes back to crash the party.
